${app_name} = servicedesk


----- Database Connection ------
1. copy tomcat conf/server.xml from /setup/server/tomcat/conf/server.xml
2. concat setup/server/tomcat/conf/local_catalina.properties to conf/catalina.properties
    - ${app_name}.db.url
    - ${app_name}.db.username
    - ${app_name}.db.password

------ Keystore ------
1. copy /setup/keystore/dev/aes-keystore.jck to /opt/keystore/aes-keystore.jck
2. concat setup/server/tomcat/conf/local_catalina.properties to conf/catalina.properties
    - ${app_name}.aesKeystore.storePass
    - ${app_name}.aesKeystore.path

------ JVM Option (local development only) ------
Add VM Option for local development
-Dcom.sun.jndi.ldap.object.disableEndpointIdentification=true




------ Server Deployment Setup ------
1. copy deploy_${app_name}.sh to /home/root
2. copy setup/server/WEB-INF to /home/root

------ Server Deployment ------
1. upload ${app_name}.war to sysop
2. run deploy_${app_name}.sh